gory:German anthems]]\n[[Category:German Empire]]\n[[Category:National symbols of Germany]]\n[[Category:French anthems]]\n[[Category:National anthem compositions in F major]]\n", "name_user": "Secondoption", "label": "safe", "comment": "Fixed apostrophs", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Els%C3%A4ssisches_Fahnenlied"}
